</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-24_ pf-text-1">In 2022, the MCA conducted over 12,000 inspections and surveys, enhancing maritime safety.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-26_ pf-text-1">The MCA coordinates search and rescue operations, responding to over 22,000 incidents annually.








</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-28_ pf-text-1">The UK boasts over 10,500 miles of coastline, necessitating robust maritime oversight.









