</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-34_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-35_ pf-text-1"><strong>Maritime safety </strong>- Measures and regulations aimed at preventing accidents and protecting lives at sea.

</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-37_ pf-text-1"><strong>Maritime security</strong> - Protocols and actions taken to protect maritime infrastructure, vessels, and personnel from intentional harm.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-39_ pf-text-1"><strong>Environmental protection</strong> - Regulations and practices to prevent pollution and preserve marine ecosystems.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-41_ pf-text-1"><strong>Search and Rescue (SAR)</strong> - Operations coordinated by the MCA to assist vessels and individuals in distress at sea.







