</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-83_ pf-text-1"><strong>Training and education </strong>- Invest in comprehensive training programs for all maritime personnel. This will ensure everyone is aware of the latest regulations and best practices.

